ğŸ“Œ Project Overview

This project demonstrates how to deploy a simple static website using Amazon S3 Static Website Hosting.
The website is publicly accessible through an S3 endpoint without using CloudFront or Route 53, making it suitable for AWS beginner and restricted environments such as AWS VocLab / AWS re:Start.
